Usage: pmfind [options]

Discovery options:
  -m NAME, --mechanism=NAME
                        set the discovery method to use [avahi|probe=<subnet>|all]
  -r, --resolve         resolve addresses
  -s NAME, --service=NAME
                        discover services [pmcd|pmproxy|pmwebd|...|all]
  -t N.N, --timeout=N.N timeout in seconds

Reporting options:
  -q, --quiet           quiet mode, do not write to stdout
  -V, --version         display version number and exit
  -?, --help            show this usage message and exit
